# ENCReload — version-control ONLY the mod data in Assets/Databases.
# Everything else (Unity Library/Temp, game SDK, built AssetBundles, game
# Resources/Editor framework) is large and/or copyrighted game content and
# must stay out of git.

# Ignore everything at the project root by default...
/*

# ...except the gitignore itself and the Assets folder (so git can descend).
!/.gitignore
!/Assets

# Inside Assets, ignore every sibling folder...
/Assets/*

# ...except the mod databases — the only thing we track.
!/Assets/Databases
